Remove upstream `video` feed from feeds.conf.default

ImmortalWRT 25.12.0-rc2 declares the OpenWrt video feed but does not
publish video/packages.adb on downloads.immortalwrt.org, so the entry
baked into /etc/apk/repositories.d/distfeeds.list makes `apk update`
fail with 404 on every device.

--- a/feeds.conf.default
+++ b/feeds.conf.default
@@ -2,4 +2,3 @@ src-git packages https://github.com/immortalwrt/packages.git^4e8d211217db8a12825
 src-git luci https://github.com/immortalwrt/luci.git^49d83a8c4893c879c0af5f43eeea65ef8986b5c3
 src-git routing https://github.com/openwrt/routing.git^82a42869933273b95a1b9295a90880ed66ecc60b
 src-git telephony https://github.com/openwrt/telephony.git^2618106d5846a4a542fdf5809f0d3ed228ce439b
-src-git video https://github.com/openwrt/video.git^094bf58da6682f895255a35a84349a79dab4bf95
